    {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Note regarding Vancomycin dosing: Traditional dosing of 45-60 mg/kg/day frequently does not achieve target AUC in term infants and older children with normal renal function. Use of AUC24 closer to 400 µg/mL adequate for most non-CNS infections. Clin Infect Dis Jul 13 2020"
    },
